        "username": "bergwolf"
      },
      "date": "2013-02-16 13:01:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(2 inline comments)\n\nThe patch changed the references requirement of ll_dentry_open to such that references on either mnt or dentry are not required when calling ll_dentry_open. So callers in mds_readpage and mds_cleanup_pending should also be changed to match the new reference requirement and free extra references they have taken on mnt/dentry. otherwise server code may be broken by the change.\n\nThanks for spotting the issue and my apology for missing the reference requirement change in the first place.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
